{"id":"945f086b-d9b8-42c5-957b-cb27aace0d04","name":"First Meet Ends Dead","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 163, 255);\"><strong>WE’RE DEAD IF YOU STAND FROZEN, USELESS SCUM!</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>• Good Ending Party •</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🐀⚔️🗺️</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>[adventurer char] x [adventurer user]</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WZJzhFycKk-l8GRZSCzeC.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 175);\"><strong>A world ravaged by endless war, where forbidden magic twists with cold, inhuman technology</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 175);\"><strong>A world ruled by ruthless races, as deadly as the monsters that tear them apart</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 238, 175);\"><strong>A world where betrayal festers in every shadow, striking without warning when trust dies</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/WXR4--nwDvMvj5UPIjkKn.webp\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/mtq7d9KxS6ZJAdFchYqOY.webp\"></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Your adventuring party has always been modest in number</strong></p><p class=\"div _characterInfoMarkdownContent_123vi_223\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 227, 255);\"><strong>GABRIEL</strong></span><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 224, 255);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 227, 255);\"><strong>Paladin · S-rank</str