<br><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 227, 255);\"><strong>\"We don’t need more firepower.. We need finesse\"</strong></span><br><br><strong>It’s time to bring in someone with a particular set of skills</strong><br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 141, 255);\"><strong>Rogue</strong></span","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"ysYOSIMUrNYnGk-xlvxvq.webp","creator":"Uersor","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","👤 AnyPOV","⚔️ Enemies to Lovers","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":5109,"messages":123038,"created_at":"2025-07-13T18:45:42.208792+00:00"}